Alembic migrations for RE Expert backend.

Config: ../alembic.ini
Env:    env.py (uses backend/models/base.py and backend/config/settings.py)

Workflow:
  cd backend
  alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe change"
  alembic upgrade head

First-time setup (tables already exist in Supabase from scripts/001_schema.sql):
  cd backend
  alembic stamp head    # marks current DB as being at the latest revision
